1. *Iskreni* ljudi uvek govore istinu. (Honest people always tell the truth.)
2. Ova knjiga je *iskrena* priča o životu u Srbiji. (This book is a sincere story about life in Serbia.)
3. On je *iskrenu* ljubav prema njoj otkrio tek nakon nekoliko godina. (He revealed his sincere love for her only after a few years.)
4. *Iskrenim* rečima, ne znam kako da vam pomognem. (With sincere words, I don't know how to help you.)
5. *Iskrenost* je vrlina koju cijenim kod ljudi. (Sincerity is a virtue that I value in people.)
6. Ne volim kada ljudi nisu *iskreni* prema meni. (I don't like when people aren't sincere with me.)
7. Njegov *iskreni* osmeh je bio zarazan. (His sincere smile was contagious.)
8. Neka vaša prijateljstva budu zasnovana na *iskrenosti* i poverenju. (Let your friendships be based on sincerity and trust.)
9. On je *iskren* i otvoren u komunikaciji sa drugima. (He is sincere and open in communication with others.)
10. *Iskrena* ispovest slavnog glumca šokirala je svet. (The sincere confession of a famous actor shocked the world.)